{"id":717,"date":"2022-02-18T15:14:00","date_gmt":"2022-02-18T21:14:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/?p=717"},"modified":"2025-12-09T15:16:17","modified_gmt":"2025-12-09T21:16:17","slug":"theta-tau","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/posts\/2022\/2022\/theta-tau\/","title":{"rendered":"Theta Tau"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>This is part of the <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"918\">Hazing Transparency Report<\/a>, which contains <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/#terminology\">terminology definitions<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/#rules\">rules defined<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-style-elevated is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Spring 2022<\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper grid-item-min-width-150 \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n\n<p>Incident: 1\/28\/2022<br>Location: On Campus<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<p>Reported: 2\/18\/2022<br>Reported by: Hotline Report, NHQ<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<p>Investigation: Joint, initially NHQ-led<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Description<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Theta Tau active members provided alcohol to minors and hazed new members by encouraging\/coercing consumption of alcohol. New members were subjected to blindfolding, scavenger hunts, required tasks to obtain signatures and confiscation\/restricted use of electronic devices.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper  \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Rules Violations<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Article III.D.(3) &#8211; Alcohol<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Article III.B.(2)a. &#8211; Hazing<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Article III.B.(2)b. &#8211; Knowledge of Hazing<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Findings<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hazing: Consumption of Alcohol; Physical Threat; Mental Health Threat; Lack of Access to Personal Items (Phones); Sensory Deprivation<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sanctions<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Disciplinary Probation from 5\/12\/22 to 12\/12\/2023<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Loss of social privileges from 8\/12\/2022 to 12\/31\/2022<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>All active members must complete online hazing prevention module<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Chapter must complete Theta Tau alcohol education module<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Chapter must develop and provide copy of risk management plan<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Spring 2022 Description Theta Tau active members provided alcohol to minors and hazed new members by encouraging\/coercing consumption of alcohol. New members were subjected to blindfolding, scavenger hunts, required tasks to obtain signatures and confiscation\/restricted use of electronic devices.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[6],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-717","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-6"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/717","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=717"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,